{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Emalia ?] works where a lot of metal came as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At that time, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Had I known about Schindler in those days, I would done anything and everything to get into his group.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, we-- or rather, I-- had to gather pieces which were suitable for the machinery we had inside to stamp out, of all things, shovels for sweeping.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father had a job to clean them up and paint them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, at one stage, was-- I was just on top of the heap sorting out some metal at the bottom, [? being ?] down to the bottom.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I saw two others also engaged in that particular-- they had other jobs, whatever they manufactured, hinges and other things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I saw them talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, went and climbed down and I wanted to tell them, don't do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's the most dangerous thing that you can do, talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You-- you do that inside, not-- not here, outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But having the intention to tell them not to talk, I soon stood there and listened to the story of the younger one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was only there for two days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was about 16.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "His parents and the family, they were hidden with Polish people, and they were kept as long as the money, jewelry, and goodies lasted.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then they were-- had to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they were in the woods and getting hungry, so he, at one time, went to a farmer where he was successfully begging, and he got his sausage.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "His father, he knew his father wouldn't eat it, not yet, because it wasn't kosher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he would look away if his family did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And eggs and other things.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
